### Pattern 6: Module Organization by Concept

**Problem**: Large monolithic modules are hard to maintain.

**Solution**: One concept per file, 5-10 related functions:

```
docs/tests/python/rasterx/
├── basic_operations.py      # Metadata, bounds, statistics
├── transformations.py       # CRS, reprojection, warping
├── band_operations.py       # Band math, masking, combining
├── spatial_operations.py    # Clip, buffer, overlay
