└── test_*.py                # Corresponding tests
```

**NOT**:
```
docs/tests/python/rasterx/
└── utils.py                 # 50 unrelated functions ❌
```

**Benefits**:
- ✅ Easy to find relevant code
- ✅ Focused test files
- ✅ Clear imports in docs
- ✅ Maintainable over time

